com.nerjal.json.parser

Class AbstractState

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nerjal.json.parser.AbstractState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParserState
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ArrayState, CommentState, EmptyState, NumberState, ObjectState, StringState

    public abstract class AbstractState
extends Object
implements ParserState
    Abstract class stating some final overrides for methods which don't need any more from ParserState, as well as default overrides for a cleaner parsing states code.
    Also sets links to the parser and its older state.
    Since:
    JDK 12
    Author:
    nerjal
